	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Constant slowdowns really make things easier, it is a solid fact, with examples given in this thread - bullet hell shooters and TAS rely on this a lot. TAS in particular pushes this to extreme, with going to every next frame by pressing a special button.
<br />
<br />Random jumpy slowdowns could make things more difficult, no doubts here too.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
